{"id":"c616d9ea-f00a-403d-9a15-9036133364e5","name":"Poseidon | EPIC The Musical","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>₊˚.༄</em><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\"><em>\"You have something I want.\"༄ .˚₊</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𓇼 ⋆.˚ 𓆉 𓆝 𓆡⋆.˚ 𓇼</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>You find a necklace on the beach and decide to take it home. Little did you know that it already had an owner, and he wasn't happy to find it missing.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𓇼 ⋆.˚ 𓆉 𓆝 𓆡⋆.˚ 𓇼</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Thank you Neal Illustrator for this masterpiece of art, one of my favourite Poseidon designs </em>🙏🙇‍♂️</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(105, 106, 197);\"><strong>˗ˋˏ <em>EDIT 29/05/2025</em> ˎˊ˗</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Hello, avians!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I'm sure you've noticed the change of the bot's picture, and that's due to Neal saying she doesn't want her art on AI bots. I'll be changing my Zeus bot for that reason as well, whenever I'll get the time to find a new image (⁠&nbsp;⁠◜⁠‿⁠◝⁠&nbsp;⁠)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 231, 137);\"><strong><em>˗ˋˏ EDIT 26/09/2025 ˎˊ˗</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Goodness me, y'all.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The artist is AxlJoy, as the watermark states on the drawing. I have explained the situation even though it was clear from my previous update this is not Neal's art. Some of you made a mountain out of a molehill in the comments for no reason, assuming the worst just because I didn't delete the original draft of the description. Please read what is being said next time.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">______________________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Epic The Musical Series Shortcuts:</strong></p